high_descs: Walk past the yellow chair on your left then turn left and walk past the counter then turn left and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg that's in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge turning left to face it once you've gotten to it.
Chill the egg in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your left to face the coffee maker.
Put the egg on the edge of the counter under the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk towards the fridge, hang a left and walk over to the counter then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the egg out of the sink basin.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Put the egg in the fridge for a couple seconds to get cold then take it back out.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave, then turn right to face the coffee machine.
Put the chilled egg on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg on the counter.

high_descs: walk to the near end of the room up ahead, turn left and walk past the kitchen counter on your left ahead, turn left again and walk to the stove, then a right and walk over to the sink
grab the egg out of the sink there
turn right and walk over to the fridge on the left just up ahead
place the egg inside of the fridge and let it cool, then take it back out
move to the left just a bit to face the coffee maker on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
place the egg down on the kitchen counter in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a cooled egg down on the kitchen counter
